            <div class="c-listicle__label">World petrol demand has been forecast to <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/oct/16/world-petrol-demand-peak-electric-car-wood-mackenzie-oil" target="_top">peak by 2030</a>, thanks to more efficient engines and the rise of the electric car.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="c-listicle__item">
            <img class="c-listicle__icon" src="images/icon-building.png" alt="">
            <div class="c-listicle__label">To join universities, government and pension funds, more than 40 organisations associated with the Catholic Church <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2017/oct/03/catholic-church-to-make-record-divestment-from-fossil-fuels" target="_top">recently announced</a> that they are divesting from fossil fuel companies – amounting to a total divestment of <a href="https://gofossilfree.org/divestment/commitments/" target="_top">$5.5 trillion</a>.</div>
          </li>
          <li class="c-listicle__item">
            <img class="c-listicle__icon" src="images/icon-battery.png" alt="">
            <div class="c-listicle__label">Concerns about renewable energy being unable to supply baseload power are no longer valid, <a href="http://www.abc.net.au/news/science/2017-10-12/renewable-energy-baseload-power/9033336" target="_top">researchers say</a>, with a combination of existing renewable technologies capable of supplying reliable power.</div>
