          </li>
          <li class="c-listicle__item">
            <img class="c-listicle__icon" src="images/icon-seal.png" alt="">
            <div class="c-listicle__label">Last year, in net additions, <a href="https://www.iea.org/renewables/" target="_top">164 gigawatts of renewable energy</a> came on line around the world, compared with 57 gigawatts of coal.</div>
          </li>
